    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Head pattern coloration. Lestes forficula: (A) male, (B) female; L. minutus: (C) male, (D) female; L. tenuatus: (E) male, (F) female; L. helix: (G) male; L. jerrelli: (H) male." ;
